article.headline: Pullian's 28 lead Milwaukee past Robert Morris 78-75

article.linkText: Pullian's 28 lead Milwaukee past Robert Morris 78-75
article.story: MILWAUKEE -- — Kentrell Pullian had 28 points and Erik Pratt scored 27 in Milwaukee's 78-75 victory over Robert Morris on Friday night. Pullian was 8-of-13 shooting, including 1 for 4 from 3-point range, and went 11 for 13 from the foul line for the Panthers (6-7). Erik Pratt added five rebounds. Elijah Jamison shot 3 for 7 (0 for 3 from 3-point range) and 1 of 4 from the free-throw line to finish with seven points. The Colonials (4-10) were led in scoring by Markeese Hastings, who finished with 24 points and six rebounds. Robert Morris also got 14 points and eight rebounds from Stephaun Walker. Alvaro Folgueiras also had 12 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
